    dc:description "FIGURE 30. A, B, Domecia acanthophora (Desbonne in Desbonne & Schramm, 1867). A, Habitus, dorsal view, juvenile female, cl 3.1 mm, cw 4.9 mm (MZUSP 41302). B, male, 6.2 mm, cw 8.8 mm, from Alagoas, Brazil. C, Domecia africana Guinot in Manning & Holthuis, 1981, female, cl 6 mm, cw 8.2 mm, from Cape Verde. B, C, after Guinot (1964). Photograph (A) by A. Pol." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7626253/files/figure.png" ;
